description: Major drums rework. Fixed some of the rhythms that were off. There are actually a lot of ghosted snare notes in the original track, but sadly GP5 can't process them. Altered/fixed a few guitar licks, specifically the tapping at 73 and the arpeggios in 101-137. There are still a couple scales that are off in 47 and 51 but I didn't have time to fix them.
title: Satch Boogie
